   <td><IMG SRC="../img/blankdot.gif" WIDTH=20 HEIGHT=1 BORDER=0 ALT=""></td>
   <td><font size="-1"><b>Films 1792046 - 1792048; 1842-1895. Film 1183504; 1941.</b></font><br>
   Jewish records of births, marriages and deaths for Bardejov, Slovakia, (formerly B&acirc;artfa, 
   S&acirc;aros, Hungary and surrounding communities, including Zborov and Smilno. The text is in
   German and Hungarian. The records are divided among several (about sixteen in all) sections or 
   books on the microfilms. These are referred to as <b>items</b>. The breakdown below is still 
   incomplete. Please refer to <a href="zborov.htm">Zborov</a> records as well, for additional 
   vital records from this area of Saros county. These records can be found at the archives in 
   Presov. The 1941 list was transcribed by Abraham L. Grussgott.
<a name="1792046"></a><PRE>
   Birth           1852-1882 ------------------------- <a href="https://familysearch.org/search/film/004405839?cat=701299" target="_blank">1792046</a>
   Marriage        1852-1882                           items 2-5
   Death           1853-1882
   Birth           1843-1853
   Marriage        1842-1853
   Death           1842-1853
   Birth           1854-1865
   Marriage        1855-1873
   Birth           1865-1874
   Death           1854-1873
   Birth           1886</pre><a name="1792047"></a>
<pre>   Birth           1886-1895 ------------------------- <a href="https://familysearch.org/search/film/004405840?cat=701299" target="_blank">1792047</a>
   Birth           1874-1885
   Marriage        1886-1895; 1920-1923
   Death           1886-1895
   Marriage        1886-1895, 1921-1922
   Death           1886-1895
   Birth           1862-1863
