   Birth, Marriage, Death     1894-1895
                             ------------------------ <a href="https://familysearch.org/search/film/004406771?cat=701299" target="_blank">1792048</a>
                                                      item 1
</pre><a name="1183504"></a><pre>
   Complete 1941 registration of the Jews of Bardejov,
   Slovakia; formerly B&acirc;artfa, S&acirc;aros, Hungary. This
   forced registration was done by the Slovak government
   before their deportation to concentration camps in Poland.
                             ------------------------ 1183504
                                                      items 3-4
</PRE>
